data.value: To start monitoring mode, please start this application with the following command line "-Monitor=<time interval>" If you start it with "-Monitor", without sepecifying an time interval, the monitor runs once and then ends. This is usefull when starting it periodically from the Task Scheduler This is an Single Instance Application, so even if you run it multiple times, only the first instance is actaully running
